---
layout: base
title: Projects
description: Independent research, interactive tools, and experimental journalism from The Freethinking Times.
permalink: /projects/
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: var(--space-12); padding-bottom: var(--space-16);">

  <header style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10); padding-bottom: var(--space-6); border-bottom: 3px solid var(--color-ink);">
    <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-masthead); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3.815rem); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Projects</h1>
    <p style="font-size: var(--text-lg); color: var(--color-ink-muted); font-style: italic; max-width: 60ch; line-height: var(--leading-normal);">
      Interactive tools, historical databases, and research projects that go beyond
      the article format. Each project is a living document — updated as new material emerges.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="projects-grid">
    {% for project in projects.index %}
    <a href="{{ project.url }}" class="project-card">
      <h2 class="project-card__title">{{ project.title }}</h2>
      <p class="project-card__description">{{ project.description }}</p>
      <span class="project-card__status">{{ project.status }} · {{ project.launched }}</span>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

</div>
